"        :nx=V9600:tc=std.19200:\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/serialcomms/_index.adoc:671
msgid ""
"For a 28.8 Kbps modem, or to take advantage of compression on a 14.4 Kbps "
